we use it for all sorts of purposes,

00:46:55.250 --> 00:46:59.190
but the most importance use for water

00:46:59.190 --> 00:47:01.495
is that it's home for
most of life on earth.

00:47:01.495 --> 00:47:06.310
Perhaps 97% of life on earth
is out there in the ocean.

00:47:06.310 --> 00:47:10.478
It keeps us alive, shapes
the way the world works,

00:47:10.478 --> 00:47:14.795
and until we face up to it
