00:47:14.795 --> 00:47:19.720
our lives are on the line, at risk.

00:47:19.720 --> 00:47:23.896
I love going out and
diving with whale sharks.

00:47:23.896 --> 00:47:27.170
It's fairly recently that
I've had a chance to do that

00:47:27.170 --> 00:47:30.476
because only recently have
we identified a few places

