was to go out and kill wildlife,

00:56:37.936 --> 00:56:41.733
cut the trees and all of
that, but now we know.

00:56:41.733 --> 00:56:45.008
We should be able to
capitalize on our big brains

00:56:45.008 --> 00:56:46.850
and figure it out.

